# Capacitor examples — ignore deps and web build output. The native projects (ios/, android/) ARE
# committed; each platform's own .gitignore (generated by `npx cap add`) excludes Pods/, build/,
# .gradle/, DerivedData, and the synced web assets (public/). After clone: `npm install` → `npx cap sync`.

# deps
**/node_modules/

# web build output (vite → dist/, Angular → dist/browser/, Capacitor copy → www/)
**/dist/
**/www/
**/out-tsc/

# misc
.DS_Store
*.log
*.tgz
